      <title>高盛认为尼日利亚奈拉将延续世界领先的涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/usd-ngn-nigerian-naira-could-extend-rally-to-below-1000-dollar-goldman-sachs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团经济学家表示，尼日利亚奈拉可能会继续上涨，使其成为本月全球表现最好的货币。只要政策制定者保持在正轨上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/usd-ngn-nigerian-naira-could-extend-rally-to-below-1000-dollar-goldman-sachs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:34:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
